PEOPLE
v.
VENEGAS S221923 Supreme Court of California October 12, 2016

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Werdegar, Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 2/5. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Fuentes (2016) 1 Cal.5th 218, 204 Cal.Rptr.3d 818, 375 P.3d 928, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)
